ActBoards of Trade Act
PrecisApproval for THE BOARD OF TRADE OF PARRSBORO in Nova Scotia (a) to change its name to THE PARRSBORO AND DISTRICT BOARD OF TRADE; and (b) to change the boundaries of its district to the town of Parrsboro, Apple River, Southampton and Bass River.
